## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **nivolumab + ipilimumab CheckMate 743 2020** = first FDA dual IO 1L mesothelioma. 20+ year pem/cis era 종료의 paradigm shift. sarcomatoid + biphasic 에 특히 OS benefit. quantum-VQE 의 PD-1/CTLA-4 dual blockade 가 fit.
2. **pembrolizumab + chemo KEYNOTE-483 2024** = 1L expansion — chemo + IO combo paradigm 확립. nivo+ipi vs pembro+chemo first-line choice 이슈.
3. **pemetrexed + cisplatin Alimta 2004** = first 1L mesothelioma — TS + DHFR + Pt 20+ year 표준. carboplatin substitution toxicity 낮춤. cytotoxic-only era 가 2020 까지 지속.
4. **bevacizumab MAPS 2016 EU off-label** = anti-VEGF + pem/cis 만성 일부 mesothelioma. atezo+bev+chemo research 단계. VEGF-axis mesothelioma 의 limited role.
5. **BAP1 가족성 mesothelioma + germline BAP1 syndrome** = inherited mesothelioma + uveal melanoma + RCC + cholangiocarcinoma cross-link. PARP synthetic lethality + EZH2 dependence target. cross-inherited_adult.
6. **mesothelin CAR-T + ADC anetumab ravtansine + CRS-207 listeria vaccine** = mesothelin-targeted 3-modality. solid tumor CAR-T 의 mesothelioma 가 prototype. quantum-VQE 의 mesothelin epitope 결합 직접 fit.
7. **asbestos exposure 만성 30-50 year latency** = chrysotile + amphibole asbestos + erionite + carbon nanotube emerging risk. K-mesothelioma 환경법 + 산정특례 + 노출 framework. cross-environmental + climate_health + occupational.
8. **HIPEC peritoneal mesothelioma cytoreduction** = surgical + heated chemo intraoperative. peritoneal mesothelioma OS benefit. epithelioid histology favorable.
9. **EPP vs pleurectomy/decortication** = surgical 논쟁 — MARS trial EPP 결과 부정적. P/D 가 현재 표준. surgical 적응증 epithelioid + early-stage 한정.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, mesothelioma 임상 의미 한정. BAP1-mutated + IO + mesothelin ADC 결합 research-stage 연결만 가능.

